Sao Paulo FC  denied it approached
British soccer player David Beckham, spokesman Felipe Espindola
said in a telephone interview.  Goal.com reported earlier Beckham rejected a request to
transfer to the Brazilian soccer team.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
